    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a reliable choice for someone looking for a functional car at a reasonable price. While it runs and drives, there are visible signs of wear including several scratches on the body and some staining on the interior upholstery. Mechanically, the engine is steady, though it may require a tune-up soon, and the suspension feels a bit soft. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that has served its previous owner well but now needs a bit of cosmetic and mechanical TLC to bring it back to its best.",
