    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding challenge? This vehicle is the ultimate project for a talented mechanic or restoration enthusiast! While it currently needs extensive mechanical and cosmetic work, it offers a solid starting point for someone looking to build a car exactly how they want it. Grab this opportunity to save a classic and make it your own!",
